
* A chat webapp called "ThyTalk"
  
- Forum where people get to exchange about latest news. 

API
https://gnews.io/ 


Functionalities:

Server side API:
- Posting comments
- Replying to posts
- Liking / Disliking posts or replys to posts
  
Outside API:
- Get latest breaking news
- Like some articles


Data input processing: 
    [maybe Using Jupyter], building a db of selected articles by a user, 
    gathering words that repeat the most often (as of 3 times up to 10 times)

    From there updating a user's attached table with their favorite keywords
    Run searches for the user and customize their news page

    recording their search keywords as well and updating keywords lists accordingly



